T1  - Insect Introductions and Diet Changes in an Endemic Hawaiian Amphidromous Goby, Awaous stamineus (Pisces: Gobiidae)
JO  - Pacific Science
SN  - 0030-8870
VL  - 47
IS  - 1
SP  - 43
