T1  - Diurnal Pattern of Salt Secretion in Leaves of the Black Mangrove, Avicennia marina, on the Sinai Coast of the Red Sea
JO  - Pac Sci
SN  - 0030-8870
VL  - 47
IS  - 1
SP  - 51
